  Point directly to Qt5 tools to fix bug #532600, and actually build
  experimental mkvtoolnix-gui.

  19 Jan 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> mkvtoolnix-7.4.0-r1.ebuild,
  mkvtoolnix-7.5.0.ebuild:
  Change the virtual/rubygems dependency to refer to the RUBY_TARGET in
  preparation of removing the version-specific slots.

  06 Jan 2015; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> mkvtoolnix-7.5.0.ebuild:
  Add build support for ruby-2.2 (bug #535738).

